<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وابن ماجه <span class="c2">(٢/ ٧٨١)</span> وابن الأعرابي <span class="c2">(١٣٨٢)</span> والبيهقي <span class="c2">(٨/ ٣٤١ - ٣٤٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
